Test Case 03: Service Detail

Test Case Title: Account Verification

Test Case ID: Account Setup - 03

Description: Verify that users can Update their operating day and operating hours.

Preconditions:
The user is logged in and on the application's home screen.

Test Steps:
Click on the add your service details at the top corner
Click proceed
Select your operating days 
Selct your operating time 
Click save

Expected Results:
User should be able to provide operating days and operating time

Actual Result: 
User is able to provide operating days and operating time
